{
  "stem": "26609.3",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "They-- I don't know how many were [INAUDIBLE] of them, but a number of, I don't know, divisions or how you call them, Italians, came to Lwow, worked hand in hand with the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know that from the history.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] They were-- they were part of Poland where they stood there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "One side was Park [INAUDIBLE] it was called, I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was a huge park.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And there were buildings-- or they build them especially for the German troops.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The other side nearby were the Italians.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I don't know how he got them because I told you before that they took people to work there.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "It was not known then.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We didn't know about the concentration camps.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So somehow, my brother-in-law got employed by the Italians because he knew Italian.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they kept him in their [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "How do you call the [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Camp.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Like a camp it was, yes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They kept him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He told them-- they were not anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Or-- so they went with the Nazis but they were not-- the people, the army, was not-- the Italian was not anti-Semitic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He told them-- they knew that he's Jewish.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He told-- they liked him because he understood their language and others and German as well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he told-- told them that he has a wife and a child.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He can't leave them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were already in the ghetto then.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was the beginning of the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was then when I was there for two weeks in the ghetto only.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He told them that if they could help him to hide somewhere in their camp.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They said, yes, bring it over.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Next day when he went to-- but he can't-- he didn't stay there overnight.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
